description: Try our easy to follow Chocolate Mousse recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chocolate Mousse Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Chop cold eggs and fold pieces through mousse. Spoon into glasses or dishes and refrigerate for 2 hrs, until set and well chilled.
